* Needed packages:

  If you are running a system different than
  Cinux, you need to check weather you have
  bison and flex installed to your system, if
  you don't, please install them otherwise 
  you won't be able to build this package.

* Compile the package:

  ./configure --prefix=/usr &&
  make

* Install the package

  make install &&
  install -v -m755 -d /usr/share/doc/libpcap-1.0.0 &&
  install -v -m644 doc/*{html,txt} /usr/share/doc/libpcap-1.0.0

  If you are building on a system different than 
  Cinux, use "sudo" 